这种形式主义罔顾科学的粗暴做法，不仅可能伤害学生身体健康，也会给疫情防控添乱。
This formalism ignores the science of rough practices, not only may harm the health of students, but will also add to the disease prevention and control.
文 | 沈 林在国家卫健委发布的系列新冠肺炎治疗方案中，一直强调中西医结合。
Shen Lin has always emphasized the combination of Chinese and Western medicine in a series of treatments for new crown pneumonia released by the National Fitness Council.
临床证明，中医经验方在减轻发热咳嗽症状、控制病情进展，提升人体免疫力方面有独特优势。
Clinical proof, TCM experience in reducing the symptoms of fever and cough, control the progress of the disease, improve human immunity has a unique advantage.
不过，日前云南临沧市教育体育局强制临沧市各中小学校服用“大锅药”的“霸道”通知，却引发了云南省临沧市部分学生家长的强烈不满——2月28日，临沧市政府召开全市复教复课疫情防控专项准备工作会议，市委副书记、市长张之政在会上讲话强调，要认真落实精准防控精准施策要求，采取积极有效的防控措施，全力做好2020年春季学期开学准备工作，防止疫情在校园发生，保障师生生命安全和身体健康。
However, the Education and Sports Bureau of Lincang City, Yunnan Province, forced schools to take "big pot medicine" notice on February 28, the city's deputy secretary and mayor Zhang Zheng stressed that the city's deputy secretary, Mayor Zhang Zheng, should earnestly implement the exact prevention and control of epidemic diseases.
2月29日，临沧市临翔区教育体育局、临沧市第二中学等单位和学校相继下发通知，要求师生及家长喝“大锅药”，以增强身体抵抗力，为受到新冠病毒疫情影响的复教复课做准备。
On February 29, the Linxiang District Education and Sports Bureau, Lincang City Secondary School and other units and schools issued circulars, teachers and students and parents to drink "big pot medicine," to strengthen physical resistance and prepare for the resumption of classes affected by the new crown virus outbreak.
通知下发后，有自称是临沧市临翔区的家长网友，提供了幼儿园内部群聊记录，群聊中有内容提到：“自3月1日起家长每天下午5点以前须上传喝药照片到班级群”。
"Since March 1, parents must upload photos of drinking pills to class groups before 5: 00 pm every day," the group said.
在通知里，幼儿园除了要求学生每天上传喝药图片外，还需写明“喝药后有无异常，如拉肚子、头晕等”，引发家长的恐慌甚至愤怒。
In the notice, kindergarten students are not only required to upload pictures of drinking medicine, but also to write "after drinking any abnormalities, such as diarrhea, dizziness," causing panic and even anger among parents.
对此，有法律专家表示强制服药可能存在违反《药品管理法》、《基本医疗卫生与健康促进法》等的风险，情节严重的，可能触犯刑法。
In this regard, legal experts have indicated that compulsory medication may involve a risk of infringement of the Pharmaceutical Administration Act, the Basic Health Care and Health Promotion Act, etc., which may constitute an offence under criminal law.
“一旦因上述情况出现了群体性不良反应事件，该规定的决策者和执行者要承担责任，可能涉嫌的罪名有：滥用职权罪、非法行医罪等。
"In the event of an incident of adverse mass reaction as a result of the above, the decision-makers and implementers of this provision are liable for possible offences such as abuse of authority, illegal practice of medicine, etc.
”该通知被曝光后，3月2日，云南临沧紧急纠正了强制师生服用“大锅药”错误做法，并发布了《关于临沧市学校师生服用“大锅药”情况通报》。
"The notice came to light on March 2, when Yunnan's Lincang emergency corrected the practice of forcing teachers and students to take" big pot medicine "and issued an information circular on the use of" big pot medicine "by teachers and students in schools in Lincang.
临沧市教体局表示，服药一事基于自愿原则；争议做法，系个别教体局、市直学校开展，目前“暂不执行原通知”，开学时间已延期。
The department said the practice was based on the principle of voluntariness. The dispute, which was conducted by individual education bureaux and municipal schools, was "temporarily suspended" and the start of the school year had been postponed.
“给师生家长带来不便，在社会上造成不良影响，在此深表歉意、深刻检讨。
"I apologize for the inconvenience caused to parents and students and the negative impact on the community.
”此外，临沧市教体局还表示，大锅药并不能预防新冠肺炎，推出目的系提高师生免疫力。
In addition, the Lincang Education and Sports Bureau said big pot medicine did not prevent pneumonia, launched to improve the immunity of teachers and students.
临沧当地人士介绍，每到换季时，学生常被组织起来统一喝“大锅药”，“已经是一种习惯和传统”。
Lincang local people introduced, each season, students are often organized to drink "big pot medicine", "has been a custom and tradition."
除临沧外，云南多地医疗机构向抗疫一线工作人员免费赠饮过“大锅药”，“大锅药”在云南等地由来已久，部分当地居民也将之用来预防疾病、增强身体免疫力。
Besides Lincang, many medical institutions in Yunnan have given free "big pot medicine" to front-line staff against the disease. "Big pot medicine" has long been used in Yunnan and other places to prevent diseases and strengthen immunity.
“大锅药”，一般指用大锅熬制的传统民族民间中医药。
"Big pot medicine" refers to the traditional Chinese medicine made in a large pot.
北京中医药大学中药学院教授翟华强接受媒体采访时表示，唐宋时期官方就有将固定成药发放给百姓用来防治瘟疫的传统，“就目前公布的成人方剂来看，十七味药的药性较为平和，剂量也比较小，药物大多属于食药两用，服用比较安全，也是有一定疗效的。
In an interview with the media, Zhai Huaqiang, a professor at the School of Traditional Chinese Medicine at Beijing TCM University, said there was a tradition in the Tang and Song Dynasties to distribute fixed medicines to people to combat the plague.
”因此，他认为特殊时期熬“大锅药”不应该反对，但也需要注意不能“以偏概全”，强制执行。
Therefore, he argues, special periods of "big pot medicine" should not be opposed, but also need to be careful not to "generalize" and enforce.
新闻图上海市第一人民医院针灸科寿崟医生也向《新民周刊》表示，“大锅药”的药方虽然问题不大，但还是要看个人体质，中医讲究“辨证施治、一人一方”，但绝不是一刀切地要求每个人喝中药：“新闻里说当地有这种传统，公序良俗的事情我们不去评价；但是该学校把吃大锅药当成入学条件，强制执行令群众反感。
"Although the prescription is not a big problem, it still depends on individual constitution," said Dr. Mao Zedong, a doctor with acupuncture at Shanghai's First People's Hospital. "TCM emphasizes" dialectical treatment, one person, "but it is not a one-size-fits-all prescription.
并且，这次的大锅药是要家长自行去药房购买，无形中给群众添加了经济负担。
Moreover, this time the big pot medicine is to parents to buy their own pharmacies, inadvertently added to the financial burden to the masses.
”2月29日的国务院新闻发布会上，北京地坛医院中西医结合科主任医师王融冰也强调，此前推荐的一些药物都是针对症状的治疗，并不是为了预防，“不主张没有症状的人使用中成药预防，没有意义”。
Wang Rongbing, director of the Department of Chinese and Western Medicine at Beijing's Ditan Hospital, also stressed that some of the drugs previously recommended were symptomatic rather than preventive. "People without symptoms are not advised to use Chinese patent medicine for prophylaxis and have no meaning," Wang said.
况且，云南临沧市远未到需要人人喝药来预防新冠肺炎的程度。
Moreover, the city of Lincang in Yunnan is far from reaching the point where everyone needs drugs to prevent new crown pneumonia.
截至2月28日，临沧市累计报告确诊病例1例，且早已治愈出院超过两周，此外无疑似病例。
As of February 28, a cumulative total of one confirmed case was reported in Lincang City and has been cured for more than two weeks, with no suspected cases.
除了可能的输入型风险外，临沧内部的扩散风险并不高，要求人人喝中药，实在有些过犹不及了。
In addition to the possible input type of risk, the proliferation risk is not high in Lincang, requiring everyone to drink Chinese medicine, is a bit too much.
正如光明日报所指出的：当地教育局也好，学校也罢，在做任何决定的时候，都首先需要考虑学生的健康，而非打着防疫的旗号做些胡乱的决策。
As the Guangming Daily pointed out, when making any decision, whether by the local education bureau or by schools, students' health should be taken into account first, rather than making random decisions under the banner of vaccination.
这种形式主义罔顾科学的粗暴做法，不仅可能伤害学生身体健康，也会给疫情防控添乱。
This formalism ignores the science of rough practices, not only may harm the health of students, but will also add to the disease prevention and control.
征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Call for orders The New People's Weekly is now soliciting interviews and true stories from all over the country: If you are a healthcare worker or family member involved in the fight against the outbreak, we hope to hear your "epidemic" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
如今，各行各业开始陆续有序复工，如何在疫情中有序恢复经济生产，我们希望了解其中的困难，或是暖心故事。
We would like to know the difficulties or heartwarming stories of how to resume economic production in an orderly fashion in all walks of life.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
